overview: Five gold stars may signify the crme de la crme when it comes to hotel ratings, but there isnt a rating high enough for the charged sex that explodes from Titans Five Star. A classic cast of hairy-chested, stubble-faced studs partake in the kind of sweat-covered, muscle-heaving, man-on-man sex that Titan delivers so well. Five Star is two hours of wall-to-wall sex that doesnt stop for chit-chat, and casually dispenses with any plot.
title: Five Star
